        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Expert Repairs</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Our skilled mechanics provide professional repair and maintenance services to keep your bike in top condition.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
